A test bed for code to use in FontFactory

Create a program using Missy's birthday and anniversary lists
to create a PDF list by DOY.

Procedures:

+ use CSV-Autoclass to create a new pipe-separated file format
  which can handle each type based on file name:

  - owner-anniversaries.csv
  - owner-birthdays.csv

+ convert old-format files to CSV

+ read the existing CSV files for an owner and create
  the single PDF list

  - use code from the xmas PostScript project 
    and module PDF::Combiner as a start


